{"tid":954963,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"Lonely Christmas","createTime":"2018-12-25T04:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T08:05:07.000Z","uid":2794,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb47739433b6c26602ec257a3a2364969bb4e0a","tid":954963,"uid":2794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:58:44.000Z","msg":"誰又騎著那鹿車飛過<br />\n忘掉投下那禮物給我<br />\n凝視那燈飾 只有今晚最光最亮<br />\n卻照亮我的寂寞<br />\n<br />\n誰又能善心親一親我<br />\n由唇上來驗證我幸福過<br />\n頭上那飄雪 想要棲息我肩膊上<br />\n到最後也別去麼<br />\n<br />\nMerry Merry Christmas<br />\nLonely Lonely Christmas<br />\n人浪中想真心告白 但妳只想聽聽笑話<br />\nLonely Lonely Christmas<br />\nMerry Merry Christmas<br />\n明日燈飾必須拆下<br />\n換到歡呼聲不過一剎<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RJbmHG4pXuA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRJbmHG4pXuA&d=SRlMtRg31rN53dMXQMtoohOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a7d41547\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RJbmHG4pXuA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bc80a8b25c2a41ddef18d796f24fe0ca516ded","tid":954963,"uid":191467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"廢<br />\n聖誕緊係返工啦"},{"pid":"60c65aa4b1e39660064d958cb9183c51e373437f","tid":954963,"uid":2794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5bc80a8b25c2a41ddef18d796f24fe0ca516ded","tid":954963,"uid":191467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"廢<br />\n聖誕緊係返工啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T06:07:57.000Z","msg":"哭了"},{"pid":"f73cf46aff83a5e0600c673b94cee879221f3b6d","tid":954963,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWRyPHe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWRyPHe.gif&h=cfe1b34a&s={SIZE}\" 